Name: Walkover
About the game: The ultimate Splatter-Strategy-Action-Game. Fight side by side with your friends against hords of Aliens. Be prepared for epic battles with several hundreds of enemies. 6 different Gamemodes (Standard, Survival, Deathmatch (with and without Aliens), Capture the flag (with and without Aliens)) 4 different weapons (Laser, Ion, Grenade, Rockets) with a total of 14 different fire modes Netcode, which allows thousands of Aliens to fight agains together with other players around the world Dedicated Game server to join, or host your own server for your friends Free2Play, Really? YES! There is no ingame currency, no paid DLC. Download, Play, Have Fun!
